{"tid":837214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港共產黨參選　陳浩天做總書記？","createTime":"2018-09-26T08:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T10:30:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c06ff8975f9340300078383477d87dfbc9c2412f","tid":837214,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2165000/2168153/biln20161118009_1024_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2165000%2F2168153%2Fbiln20161118009_1024_1024_1024.jpg&h=4c25db18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消息指「香港共產黨」擬邀陳浩天做總書記。<br />\n<br />\n根據「香港共產黨」專頁，他們提及「堅持反對基本法實行有關資本主義制度的條文」，又指「不排除武裝起義」。政圈中更有傳，他們正邀請香港民族黨召集人陳浩天，擔任「香港共產黨總書記」一職。<br />\n<br />\n對於政圈有傳，該「香港共產黨」專頁是由楊繼昌牽頭成立，但楊向傳媒否認，稱這只是網民受他啟發，而他本人並沒有加入該組織。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2168153/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E3%80%80%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9%E5%81%9A%E7%B8%BD%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2168153%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%2581%259A%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A8%2598%25EF%25BC%259F&d=vqf9ZX9Fm6encRDPqvqyrP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=951cd333\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2168153/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E3%80%80%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9%E5%81%9A%E7%B8%BD%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"be5e4ea64dafefb47035e41d5a5df0b2eb135107","tid":837214,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:30:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想打對台？</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/48/習近平.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F48%2F%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3.jpg&h=87618c49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6decabdb60e45ee42b4f3433f66cc278abe9118d","tid":837214,"uid":138214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"唔係條垃圾楊繼昌搞架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e35a68cd425316e75c27a3fd7e5cb41308dda97","tid":837214,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}